methods.name: put
methods.comment:
Puts the given Object in the Object array at
 the given index

methods.name: remove
methods.comment: Sets the value at the given index to null.

params.name: index
params.comment: the index to set to null.

methods.name: findLastNonZeroIndex
methods.comment: Finds the index of the last non-null value.

return.comment:
The index of the last non-null value. 0 will be returned
 if the array is empty.

methods.name: get
methods.comment: Returns the Object at the given index

return.comment:
The Object value at the given index. A null will
 be return for any index not initialized to
 another value.
